name: Plonk Crazy Golf - Borough Market
description: Plonk at Borough is a very relaxed place. An area for Arcade is very spacious, currently there are two air hockey, two foosball tables, one table tennis, four video arcade cabinets with multiple game choices each, Aliens shooter (on FreePlay), and two Pinball Machines(!) which are serviced quite often (that's what I noted). For those who like Classic Arcade video games with a touch of pinball, this location is definitively worth a visit.
